1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:06,440
What are you waiting for?

2
00:00:06,440 --> 00:00:11,840
Pluck your hair and make an offer!

3
00:00:11,840 --> 00:00:19,760
Hey, hey, wait!

4
00:00:19,760 --> 00:00:35,520
I, the keeper of Black Wind Mountain, have long been waiting for your arrival.

5
00:00:35,520 --> 00:00:43,120
Oh, his spitting image, I'd say.

6
00:00:43,120 --> 00:00:49,720
Up ahead is Guan Yin Temple.

7
00:00:49,720 --> 00:01:02,600
Once it was bustling with worshippers before it was ruined by that fire.

8
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:13,400
Ah, then the temple was rebuilt.

9
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:19,700
What good is it to rebuild a temple if the goodwill of men has been tarnished?

10
00:01:19,700 --> 00:01:21,700
It's burned to ashes.

11
00:01:21,700 --> 00:01:26,940
Oh, no, no, no.

12
00:01:26,940 --> 00:01:30,940
You've forgotten this place, but they haven't forgotten you.

13
00:01:30,940 --> 00:01:34,840
Oh, quick, get away, get away.

14
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:35,840
That's a tough one.

15
00:01:35,840 --> 00:01:37,580
Good luck to you!

